ssets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13247777d71188027b1cd992116055ccf4dbec36","tid":85111,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64e01b534f64044a488e1de22cb25b6c06ff8981","tid":85111,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"畢業於香港理工大學酒店及旅遊業管理學院的廖小姐，6月已開始求職，但她不擅長溝通，又怕「跑數會很大壓力」，她要求待遇僅1萬元<br />\n<br />\n年年大學INFO DAY D中學雞都狗衝"},{"pid":"4376ef3d7f15057eb7841b0e246d51a690c71de4","tid":85111,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"2個月寄得20封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63694084f1027259417e12c24bbb342e5b912eaf","tid":85111,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"狗屎人工請師傅"},{"pid":"225a937ec8351e11bee4ac3cf4cc06b82ef93ef0","tid":85111,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"跑數根本on9<br />\n俾人捽數搞到成隻狗咁<br />\n日日帶住老母返工<br />\n呢啲咁不孝嘅工我做老豆老母都唔會俾個仔做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下人地真係做開青年工作嘅機構佢地出嘅刊物啦<br />\n今期講生涯規劃<br />\n真心正<br />\n建議買番本睇下<br />\n<br />\nBreakazine! 047 未來工作想像指南<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.breakazine.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.breakazine.com&d=VXAYx0S8Fq2ve3j0i6Iwn5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7099a0b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.breakazine.com</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6bg8ei3x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6bg8ei3x&h=317e84b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回歸初心，你最想找一份怎樣的工作？<br />\n <br />\n時局在變，職場在變，<br />\n要迎向未來，香港人的工作方式，是時候改變了，<br />\nWORK，唔再係咁WORK。<br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n應該找一份怎樣的WORK？<br />\n不同人，會對你說不同的話。<br />\n <br />\n國家告訴你它的規劃藍圖，要求你捉緊發展機遇；<br />\n公司告訴你它的晉升階梯，期望你自我增值；<br />\n社會流行的成功標準，誘導你只追求薪高糧準。<br />\n來到2017年的香港，這一套，其實仲WORK唔WORK？<br />\n <br />\n今期Breakazine!訪問逾50人，問的正是，<br />\n當香港社會看似愈來愈唔WORK，我們仲係咪咁WORK？<br />\n怎樣的WORK，才回應到自己和身處的社羣？<br />\n人，其實係為咩而WORK？<br />\n <br />\n人生難以掌控，工作需要想像，<br />\n要知道怎樣WORK下去，<br />\n要聽的，其實是自己內在的聲音，<br />\n我們的初心。"},{"pid":"7b731f5de4855dc3e00425a7f4d10577d123970e","tid":85111,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"d 一房都快成仟萬.. 9K 點供"},{"pid":"68debf7be66c5fa01e3d902d15c9b77d4df6736e","tid":85111,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:47:02.000Z","msg":"人工低都好<br />\n等佢知你份人工留唔住人<br />\n得番你個工作環境留住人<br />\n講真 讀書勁果d去哂做護士<br />\n讀書廢果d去左做警犬<br />\n<br />\n我都明僱主唔係有咁多錢請人<br />\n但唔好請人番黎做狗"},{"pid":"168abda953b6a13e5c303d6353c036f401697cb7","tid":85111,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"76ad3bc75f5bcd61c7eab8bee7447e746f965b32","tid":85111,"uid":72771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:19:58.000Z","msg":"諗起當年08年金融海嘯,畢業出嚟嗰份得7800😂😥"},{"pid":"16997c02dab39596bb6cf1d5cb1e58f1fc1d2a63","tid":85111,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:22:00.000Z","msg":"幾多年前架"},{"pid":"4090c891077996c1c08df3bc31158e8ee4b43ffc","tid":85111,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畢業於香港理工大學酒店及旅遊業管理學院的廖小姐，6月已開始求職，但她不擅長溝通，又怕「跑數會很大壓力」，她要求待遇僅1萬元<br />\n<br />\n年年大學INFO DAY D中學雞都狗衝</blockquote><br />\n我年年都去睇黑絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37077ab1b9d8cd46858729e7f24db0d56b9e0058","tid":85111,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"9000食屎都唔夠啦"},{"pid":"0a420b8a8790f3100e6936154b40d1ad236f7b98","tid":85111,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:40:29.000Z","msg":"大學生多數高分低能(學術9up多),唔似我地ive生一畢業個個2萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi